WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
How do I write my homework on the computer?

00:07.000 --> 00:09.000
Can I learn?

00:09.000 --> 00:18.000
Sure. First, open a new document. Click the mouse on New Document.

00:18.000 --> 00:23.000
What's the mouse? Is this it? Yes.

00:23.000 --> 00:27.000
Where do I click on New Document?

00:27.000 --> 00:31.000
On the left of the screen, there.

00:31.000 --> 00:34.000
Okay. What's next?

00:34.000 --> 00:43.000
Next, you write your homework in the New Document. Use the keyboard.

00:43.000 --> 00:49.000
What do I do next? How do I save the document?

00:50.000 --> 00:55.000
You click Save and write a name for it.

00:55.000 --> 00:58.000
Where do I write the name?

00:58.000 --> 01:01.000
Write it in the box.

01:01.000 --> 01:06.000
Okay. Then click Save again.

01:06.000 --> 01:12.000
Okay. Finally, how do I print my document?

01:12.000 --> 01:17.000
Click Print and Okay.

01:17.000 --> 01:19.000
What about some paper?

01:19.000 --> 01:25.000
Oh yes. Of course. You put the paper in there first.

